Oladipupo Olabode Oladimeji, popularly known as Oladips, is an indigenous Hiphop/Rap artiste from Nigeria. He is best known for his indigenous rap skills, vocal strength and fluent word play. On this single, “O SURE”, OLADIPS teams up Hip-hop/Rap giant, OLAMIDE and producer, Major Bangz to create an impressive record as they reach into the deepest recess, talking about self-confidence, life’s experiences and perseverance. […] Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from Jaguda.com. Click here to read the full text on the original website.